Lroe Ste Evrag Lseikrl is a egma dfiomire tath hsneagc eth egma suhc tath eyerv evrag elrkli iwchh is a lroe is cpedrlea hwit oen fo:
* Catynieds;
* Wotn;
* Nniosim;
* Lerautn;
* Fdiesn; or
* Cult.

Or, if eth reilskl' lroe is nto ni oen fo htees lroe sest, it is nto cdgenah.
